data.description: Price Reduced!!! Motivated Seller! More acreage available!!! This wonderful custom built home on 1.75 acres (additional land available), located in the Fitzgerald Crossing area, offers 4 bedrooms 3 1/2 baths! The spacious and open concept floor-plan is great! A custom kitchen with solid surface counters, bar seating, breakfast area and formal dining all flow to make this an entertainers dream home! The split floor plan offers a Master suite with a large master bath, separate jetted tub and over-sized tile shower with convenient double vanities. This stunning home also offers a guest bedroom with on-suite full bath! Looking out the expansive windows with custom plantation shutters, you're swept by the views of beautiful rolling landscape! A private covered back porch and recently added wood deck with nice above-ground pool are bonus features of this home. Inviting curb appeal with a circle drive and nice front-porch! A new roof installed just one year ago! CALL or TEXT JASON NICHOLS at 501-951-7170 for an appointment or more information. Or, Cross County Realty at 870-238-5662.
data.whatILove: Gorgeous views, rural but convenient! Large spacious floor plan!
